title: NCAA Division I Men's Basketball Supported Programs by Institution
name: NCAA Division I Men's Basketball Supported Programs by Institution
description:
This dataset explores men's basketball at the D1 level in the NCAA. There are 329 institutions that sponsor men's basketball at the D1 level. This dataset maps them.

                        Source: http://web1.ncaa.org/onlineDir/exec/sponsorship?sortOrder=0&division=1&sport=MBB

                        Accessed on Jan 29, 2008
